criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients ≥ 18 years;

          -  Have been diagnosed positive of SARS-CoV-2 in the Virological Laboratory of Ambroise
             Paré hospital;

          -  Have been blood sampled between 1 day and 14 days from the first clinical syndromes,
             and their collections of serum or plasma are conserved and accessible;

          -  Affiliated to the social security scheme or entitled;

          -  Informed and non-opposed to participating to the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Opposition of patient to participation to the study;

          -  Foreign patients under french AME scheme.
